Package model

Class Toys

java.lang.Object
model.Toys
Direct Known Subclasses:
Animals, BoardGames, Figures, Puzzles
public abstract class Toys extends Object
The Toys class is an abstract class that provides getters and setters for various attributes of a toy. this class provides methods to format and represent the object as a string.
Version:
6.9
Author:
Caesar and Steven
